  "name": "Bioluminescent Bell",
  "mood": "Aether",
  "engines": [
    "Obrix"
  ],
  "description": "Ring Mod (proc3=RingMod) with src2 detuned 7.03 semitones creates the classic inharmonic bell partial relationship \u2014 the 2.756 ratio that produces the warmest metallic tone. Sine + Triangle sources keep the carrier pure enough for the ring modulation to dominate. Delay FX at coprime-derived timing (fx1Param 0.382 = golden ratio sub-beat). The bell glows rather than strikes \u2014 attack 0.008s, release 3.8s. VelEnv\u2192amp ensures velocity becomes expressivity, not volume.",
